{"tid":1189304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人生最痛係咪就係遺憾","createTime":"2019-06-06T17:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T14:36:37.000Z","uid":22323,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b77a5ede6fa703d77652a0cd2ac3d7d8875c6d87","tid":1189304,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"後悔當初自己無好好重視<br />\n以為一切都會順順利利<br />\n以為真係可以一齊初戀走到最尾<br />\n以為你既耐性係無限，我地既關係亦都唔會有限期<br />\n以為呢張臉會對一輩子<br />\n但原來一切都唔係咁理所當然<br />\n原來果日可能就係我地人生中見既最後一面<br />\n<br />\n雖然你我身邊都可能已經有另一半<br />\n雖然我可能已經唔再愛你<br />\n但諗起大家從最初既幸福去到最後分離不再見<br />\n總係覺得好遺憾好可惜、<br />\n大家無好好咁一齊走完呢個旅程<br />\n而且、呢個遺憾可能伴隨終生，你無辦法解決到<br />\n<br />\n大家對於遺憾、又有無咩想分享下？<br />\n斯菊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7219abc358c3f59865a0f03725e02e9945cb2f4","tid":1189304,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:30:32.000Z","msg":"生理痛先痛 無情感唔會"},{"pid":"aa997f78905ddea4b9323d251cfabc99caa51e24","tid":1189304,"uid":22323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d7219abc358c3f59865a0f03725e02e9945cb2f4","tid":1189304,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:30:32.000Z","msg":"生理痛先痛 無情感唔會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"有得簡、我會寧願比人打到仆街咁痛好過個心陰陰濕濕咁痛"},{"pid":"36fa1494b4ae0686a23f98d6766103e791f7cd4e","tid":1189304,"uid":31238,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:54:32.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro<br />\n曾經都以為同初戀 可以一直行落去 <br />\n可以一直對住佢 以為有愛可以跨過一切<br />\n但結果感情 可以好脆弱<br />\n曾經計劃 幻想既未來 所有野都有佢既身影<br />\n然而依架佢已選擇左另一個 <br />\n我總慢慢走緊出黎<br />\n個種遺憾 每次一諗起<br />\n個心就會拿住拿住 好撚辛苦 好無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30b83bb51be94c6395ab8ec430e61f010a99c6c","tid":1189304,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"係冇機會道歉嘅內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c44f68af25d195106af47c7bb2f565a6a97782","tid":1189304,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a30b83bb51be94c6395ab8ec430e61f010a99c6c","tid":1189304,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"係冇機會道歉嘅內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"唔係淨止對佢道歉<br />\n而係對當初既我地，為呢段關係而道歉"},{"pid":"1e0f667587a17167ca43b71d901467bcc4d9eea1","tid":1189304,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T20:31:14.000Z","msg":"我明呀清 一生遺憾 真係最痛<br />\n後悔點解唔再忍讓多幾步 後悔所有未夠好既細節位 如果做好左 可能就唔同晒 無啦宜家"},{"pid":"d09d7c4469f85ab509fd81eea34b597eff3bd782","tid":1189304,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0f667587a17167ca43b71d901467bcc4d9eea1","tid":1189304,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T20:31:14.000Z","msg":"我明呀清 一生遺憾 真係最痛<br />\n後悔點解唔再忍讓多幾步 後悔所有未夠好既細節位 如果做好左 可能就唔同晒 無啦宜家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T20:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/so